'''天主教委內瑞拉的聖克里斯托瓦爾教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Sancti Christophori in Venetiola}}；{{lang-es|Diócesis de San Cristóbal de Venezuela}}）是[[委內瑞拉|委內瑞拉]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教梅里達總教區|梅里達總教區]]。

教區於1922年10月12日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=XV |year=1923 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=99-102 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-15-1923-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-06-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619172728/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-15-1923-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-06-19 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，位於[[塔奇拉州|塔奇拉州]]，2010年時有1,350,000名教友（佔轄區總人口83.4%）、86個[[堂區|堂區]]和195名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-es|瑪略·德爾瓦列·莫龍塔-羅德里格斯|Mario del Valle Moronta Rodríguez}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Audiences, 08.06.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/06/08/170608.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619173618/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/06/08/170608.html |archivedate=2020-06-19 |language=en |date=2017-06-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|若望·亞爾伯·阿亞拉-拉米雷斯|Juan Alberto Ayala Ramírez}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 18.06.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/18/200618a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619145613/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/18/200618a.html |archivedate=2020-06-19 |language=en |date=2020-06-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

